            <p>• Update your account information</p>
            <p>• Add missing information</p>
            
            <p><strong>Right to Erasure ("Right to be Forgotten"):</strong></p>
            <p>• Delete your account and associated data</p>
            <p>• Remove specific pieces of information</p>
            <p>• Subject to legal retention requirements</p>
            
            <p><strong>Right to Restrict Processing:</strong></p>
            <p>• Limit how we use your information</p>
            <p>• Suspend processing while disputes are resolved</p>
            <p>• Object to certain types of processing</p>
            
            <p><strong>Right to Data Portability:</strong></p>
            <p>• Receive your data in a machine-readable format</p>
            <p>• Transfer your data to another service provider</p>
            <p>• Export your account information</p>
